subtitleNullable: First Level Care Facilities from DHIS
descriptionNullable: Access a comprehensive list of First Level Care Health Facilities in Pakistan, as reported by the District Health Information System (DHIS). This dataset provides a valuable resource for healthcare professionals, researchers, and policymakers seeking insights into the distribution and characteristics of health facilities at the first level of care across Pakistan. Ideal for studying the healthcare infrastructure and planning interventions to enhance health services at the grassroots level.
